@startuml
title Sequence 15 - Verifikasi Bukti LoA dan Buat Placement
autonumber
actor "Administrator CDA" as Admin
participant "Frontend Admin\nVerifikasi" as FE
participant "Admin Application API" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Notification Queue" as Notif

Admin -> FE: Buka halaman Verifikasi
FE -> API: GET /admin/applications/pending-verification
API -> DB: Query Applications status=ACCEPTED dengan proof_url
DB --> API: Daftar aplikasi menunggu verifikasi
API --> FE: Applications
FE --> Admin: Tampilkan bukti LoA

Admin -> FE: Verifikasi atau tolak bukti
alt bukti valid
  FE -> API: POST /admin/applications/{id}/verify {start_date,end_date}
  API -> DB: Validasi application ACCEPTED dan proof_url ada
  API -> DB: Pastikan belum ada placement untuk application_id
  API -> DB: Insert Placements status=ACTIVE
  API -> Notif: Queue notifikasi placement aktif
  DB --> API: Commit OK
  API --> FE: placement_id
  FE --> Admin: Tampilkan placement dibuat
else bukti ditolak
  FE -> API: POST /admin/applications/{id}/reject-proof {reason}
  API -> DB: Set Applications.status=OFFERED
  API -> Notif: Queue notifikasi upload ulang LoA
  DB --> API: Commit OK
  API --> FE: Bukti ditolak
end
@enduml
